snippet.title: Silent Slayer: Vault of the Vampire | Reveal Trailer | Meta Quest 2 + 3 + Pro
snippet.description:
Wishlist Silent Slayer: Vault of the Vampire in the Meta Quest Store today: https://metaque.st/3BQEeHj 

Don't make any sudden moves! Your life depends on it. 

Become a stealth vampire slayer on a mythic quest to destroy powerful sleeping monsters in this suspenseful single-player jumpscare game from Schell Games, the team behind Among Us VR and the I Expect You To Die series.
